<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Air Ticket | Prince Air Ltd</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>

<header class="header">
<div class="container">

<div class="logo">
<img src="images/logo.png" alt="Prince Air Ltd">
<h2>Prince Air Ltd</h2>
</div>

<nav class="navbar">
<a href="index.html">Home</a>
<a href="booking.html">Booking</a>
<a href="balance.html">Balance</a>
<a href="visa.html">Visa</a>
<a href="country.html">Country</a>
<a href="airticket.html">Air Ticket</a>
<a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
</nav>

</div>
</header>

<section class="services">

<div class="container">

<h1 style="text-align:center; margin:40px 0;">Air Ticket Services</h1>

<div class="card">
<i class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure"></i>
<h3>International Air Ticket</h3>
<p>We provide affordable international flight booking services.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<i class="fa-solid fa-plane-arrival"></i>
<h3>One Way Ticket</h3>
<p>Book one-way flights to your destination easily.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<i class="fa-solid fa-plane-circle-check"></i>
<h3>Round Trip Ticket</h3>
<p>Best prices for return and round-trip air tickets.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i>
<h3>24/7 Customer Support</h3>
<p>Our support team is ready to help with your bookings.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>